UGREEN Braided Lightning to 3.5 mm Headphone Jack Adapter for iPhone 12 Pro, 12 Pro Max, 11, XS Max, XR X 8 7 Plus

This Lightning to 3.5mm headphone jack adapter lets you connect devices that use a 3.5 mm audio plug to your Lightning devices. It eliminates the necessity to purchase a Lightning headphone.

Widely Compatibility:

iPhone Models: iPhone 12/12 Pro/12 mini/12 Pro Max/SE/11 Pro / iPhone 11 Pro Max / iPhone 11 / XS / XS Max / XR / X / 8 / 8 Plus / 7/ 7 Plus/ 6s/ i 6s Plus / 6 / 6 Plus / SE / 5s / 5c / 5

iPad Models:

iPad (7th generation) / iPad 9.7"(6th generation 2018) / iPad (2017) / iPad 4 / iPad 3 / iPad 2 / iPad 1

iPad Pro 12.9" / 10.5"(2nd generation), iPad Pro 12.9" / 9.7"(1st generation)

iPad Air 3 / iPad Air 2 / iPad Air (1st generation)

iPad mini 5 / mini 4 / mini 3 / mini 2 / mini

iPod Models: iPod touch (7th generation) / iPod touch (6th generation)

This Lightning to 3.5mm adapter is compatible with all Apple headphone, support audio&mic function, in line control including volume control, calling, allows you to control your music and take calls on the go

Kindly Note:

1. it can support mic, audio, calling for CTIA Android headphones, but it doesn't support volume control for CTIA Android headphones.

2. It doesn't support OMTP Android headphones.

3. It does not support the iPhone 7 former model or iPad to connect 2 headphones at the same time, because the Lightning port will stop audio output when connecting a headphone to the 3.5mm audio jack of iPhone.

UGREEN Lightning to 3.5mm Headphone Jack Adapter

Apple MFi Certified

Ensures completely and securely connect with your Apple devices, 100% compatibility to the iOS system without error message.

Powerful Functions

Allows you to Control Music (volume, previous/next), Answer Phone Calls easily, just connect audio headphone/earphone to your Apple devices with the adapter

Super Sound

Sampling rate up to 48KHz and filter out noise. provides a clear with no breaks quality sound.

Plug & Play

This adapter lets you connect devices that use a 3.5mm audio plug to your Lightning devices. Just plug the adapter in your device, let your Apple equipment recognize the adapter for 3-5 sec before playing music.

Safe and Reliable

UGREEN 3.5mm plug to Lightning cable made from original Apple chips provides a secure and stable sound transmission.

Aluminum Alloy Shell

The Lighting to 3.5mm jack dongle is made up of high quality aluminum alloy, which is durable, sleek, small and smart

Nylon-Braided Cable

Braided Outer are supple with a quality feel and durability

Reinforced Strain Relief

The Reinforced strain relief makes the cable more flexible and durable

      Product description

      Color:Grey

      UGREEN [Apple Certified ] Nylon-Braided & Aluminum Ligtning to 3.5mm Headphone Jack Adapter
      Apple MFi program certified iPhone lightning to 3.5mm jack adapter.
      Compatible for Apple devices which have a lightning connector with iOS 10.3.1 or later. ( iPhone 7 / 7 Plus / 8 / 8 Plus / X / XR / XS / XS Max ).
      Supports answer the call, volume control, pause and play, microphone functions like the original earphones.
      Sampling rate up to 48KHz and filter out noise, provides a clear with no breaks quality sound.
      Made of Hi-Q aluminum alloy shell and nylon-braided cable, built-in enameled copper and PVC jacket.
      NOTE:
      It doesn't support OMTP Android headphone.
      It doesn't support volume control for CTIA Android headphones.
      It only support IOS 10.3.1 and later.
      Package:
      1 UGREEN lightning to 3.5mm headphone jack adapter

      Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2020
      Color: GreyVerified Purchase
      I've tried at least 3 different brands. This one is a bit more expensive than the others. But the quality! The sound is brilliant. The cheapest ones often don't let the phone functions (microphone, volume, pause) work. The not-as-cheap ones have really poor sound quality, including one that only functioned reasonably if you unplug it and plug it in again each time you use it. This one works the first time I plug it in. No clicking, no humming/buzzing. It fits snug in the lightning jack and doesn't come loose if I have the phone in my pocket. But the sound quality: I have expensive wired headphones and music that needs them. This is the only lightning adapter I've tried that does it justice. Don't waste money buying and returning junk. Learn from my experience and just buy this one.

      I've amended my review a year later. I'm buying probably my 3rd or 4th one of these adapters because I lose them. My kids lose them. My dog chews on them. Stuff happens. But when I need to replace it, I just buy another. I've tried a few cheaper ones and I always end up back on this adapter.
